Package car.restrictions

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EngineAircoRestriction
    If the ultra engine is selected, you can only fit the manual airco.
    MandatoryPartsRestriction
    Body, color, engine, gearbox, seats and wheels are mandatory.
    PartialRestriction
    A partialrestriction is always 'partially fulfilled'.
    Restriction
    this class represents a setific restriction and a chain to manage all restrictions
    SportEngineRestriction
    If a car has a sports body it must have the performance or ultra engine.
    SportSpoilerRestriction
    If a car has a sport body, a spoiler is mandatory.
    StrictRestriction
    A strict restriction is partially fulfilled for a given specification if and only if it is completely fulfilled for that specification.
